    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You form an invisible tear in spacetime within 10 ft of you, which links to a location within range. The first creature of Medium size or smaller that passes through is teleported immediately to the linked location (following the same rules as Mugen Ugoku no Jutsu).<br><br>Once the technique ends, you become @Condition[fatigued]{fatigued} and must make a Fortitude save (DC 25) to avoid becoming @Condition[exhausted]{exhausted} instead.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 6 Chakra to increase the number of creatures that can pass through the gate by 1 (maximum 1, +1 per 10 levels total)</p>\n\n",
